Package: SuperSpot
Title: Simplification of spatial transcriptomic data by merging together similar spots
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Matei Teleman
Maintainer: The package maintainer <matei.teleman@unil.ch>
Description: Aggregates spatial transcriptomic data into metaspots dataset by merging together  very similar spots. 
